myblockchain-community (5.7.7-rc-3ubuntu15.04) vivid; urgency=low

  * updated Standards-Version to 3.9.6 in d/control
  * apparmor profile updated to allow read on all files under /etc/myblockchain
  * added new conf files under d/extra/*.conf
  * myblockchain_plugin moved from client to server pkg
  * innochecksum moved from client to server pkg
  * server pkg now replaces client pkg
  * added systemd service profile and script
  * new /etc/myblockchain/my.cnf management scheme added for Ubuntu 15.04
    as discussed in Dec 2014 for native packaging source
  * added dh "--with systemd" for enabling systemd
  * myblockchain-common now conflicts with
    myblockchain-server-5.6, myblockchain-server-core-5.6
    myblockchain-client-5.6, myblockchain-client-core-5.6
  * myblockchain-*-server no more provides
    myblockchain-server-5.6, myblockchain-server-core-5.6
  * myblockchain-*-client no more provides
    myblockchain-client-5.6, myblockchain-client-core-5.6

